    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义高精度角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可通过探索或击杀怪物获取的素材兑换角色、服装、武器、动作等来换装自定义性感美女角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内角色均为高精度模型和材质，皮肤细节完整，力求还原最真实的身体例如乳房丝袜等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/1920c286e04ef34fa13fe3c862a8773d.poster.avif?t=1771913442\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/1920c286e04ef34fa13fe3c862a8773d.webm?t=1771913442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/1920c286e04ef34fa13fe3c862a8773d.mp4?t=1771913442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >近战武器和枪械组合</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可通过近战武器对近距离敌人进行攻击，近战中可使用刀剑星尘粒子般的砍刀武器并附魔连击达到高伤害，也可翻滚重击、蓄力重击等迅速行动，也可格挡来自敌人的伤害，探索迷雾影黑般的场景，扮演猎人探索场景击杀怪物，搜索撤离，也可使用武器射击等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/9d46fd1fb3e7750d189448124d176ed7.poster.avif?t=1771913442\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/9d46fd1fb3e7750d189448124d176ed7.webm?t=1771913442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/9d46fd1fb3e7750d189448124d176ed7.mp4?t=1771913442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >细腻皮肤和人物模型</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人物皮肤细节清晰可见，从皮肤褶皱到壁纸般的毛孔纹理，均清晰可见，在试玩版中玩家可免费开玩探索角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257590/extras/bd79da11ba60b5096b8dac42890c4e99.avif?t=1771913442\" width=616 height=1568 /></span></p>",
